<author>mạykl ạ̹sḥạq, mạykl ạ̹sḥạq</author>
<title>ạftḥ qlby ạlqạsy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạftḥ qlby ạlqạsy wạmlk fyh yạ yswʿ
 knt bạʿysẖ wạ̉nạ nạsy mn gẖyr ạ̉y rjwʿ
 1- knt fy jhly ʿnyd rạfḍ ṣwtk ly
 wạ̉nt mạdd ly ạlgẖyd bmrạḥm smạwyẗ
 2- yạmạ smʿt ktyr wfḍlt fy kẖṭạyạy
 wrfḍt ạltgẖyyr wʿsẖt ldnyạy
 3- ạ̹blys rạbṭ ạ̹ydy bslạsl wqywd
 nfsh yfḍl sydy msẖ ʿạyzny ạ̉ʿwd
 4- wạdy dmwʿ ạltwbẗ mn ạ̹nsạn mḥtạj
 ạ̹nk tyjy wtsẖfy wtbqy̱ lnfsy ʿlạj</lyrics>
</song>